  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sponsor women entrepreneurs to start an e-business</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ShopO Invests trains and provides the technical and start-up capital for women in Nairobi to create their own cross-border, e-commerce businesses. Going way beyond the traditional microfinance model, we develop women business owners with the skills to operate in an ever-expanding digital ecommerce marketplace. Each new ShopO-wner receives a $1000 interest free loan to start her business. This loan is paid back to ShopO in 3-4 months and we use the funds to restart the cycle with another woman.</narrative>
  </description>
